Mushrooms are very versatile vegetable that are great for anytime meals. They cook fast and mushroom recipes can be dull, but add bacon, avocado, cheese stuffing’s and you can make magic. Serves 4-6 as a snack Preparation time: 10 minutes
Cooking time: 20 minutes
